  "prompt": "Should I text my crush first?",
  "response": "Deciding whether to text your crush first can depend on various factors. Here are a few things to consider:\n\n1. **Confidence and Initiative:** If you feel confident and excited about starting a conversation, go for it! Taking the initiative can show interest and confidence.\n\n2. **Previous Interactions:** Reflect on your previous interactions. If they were positive and your crush seemed engaged, texting first might be a good idea.\n\n3. **Communication Style:** Consider your crush's communication style. Do they typically respond promptly and seem happy to chat? If so, it might be a good sign to text first.\n\n4. **Message Content:** Think about what you want to say. A thoughtful or lighthearted message can be a great way to start a conversation.\n\n5. **Personal Comfort:** Ultimately, it\u2019s important to be comfortable with your decision. If texting first feels right to you, go ahead. If you\u2019re unsure, take your time to decide.\n\nRemember, a simple, friendly text can be a good way to gauge interest and start a conversation. Good luck!",
